(25546, 670, 2591, 2, '溫柔搖滾的呢喃 (Live)', '這個版本的歌曲是我們09-01-21在河岸留言的現場Live側錄版本，放上來跟大家分享～', '2009-01-21 00:00:00', 2009, 0, 1, 1, '吉他擺在窗口的平台\r\n關於那些過去的\r\n你用你的吉他彈那些平淡的口白\r\n溫柔的像大鐘的鐘擺\r\n\r\n你的吉他彈奏出一段\r\n溫柔搖滾的呢喃\r\n\r\n\r\n*Day after day 我走不出的悲 \r\n 你留下的疲憊 滿滿的眼淚\r\n 低沉而優雅的彈奏出我的傷悲\r\n\r\n Day after day 我走不出的悲\r\n 繞不完的殘缺 殘忍的責備\r\n 冷靜又暴烈的唱出了我的卑微*\r\n\r\n\r\n我站上了昏暗的舞台\r\n對於曾經回憶的\r\n我用我的歌聲唱那些說不出的無奈\r\n只為了證明你的存在\r\n\r\n你的吉他彈奏出一段\r\n溫柔搖滾的呢喃\r\n\r\n**', '', 292, '', '惟惟', '惟惟', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-06-16 00:41:55', '2015-03-12 13:42:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(25547, 670, 2591, 3, 'Broken Home (Live)', '這個版本的歌曲是我們09-01-21在河岸留言的現場Live側錄版本，放上來跟大家分享～', '2009-01-21 00:00:00', 2008, 0, 1, 7, 'When she was seven\r\nShe dreamt that one day her life would just change.\r\nAll of her sorrows would just burn away,\r\n\r\nLike ashes in a flame,\r\nBut on that very same day,\r\nShe answered the phone,\r\nTo find her mom had just passed away.\r\n\r\nMommy, please don’t leave me,\r\nHere alone with daddy\r\nIn this broken home.\r\nDaddy hates me,\r\nHe’s angry and he hurts me.\r\n\r\nThe days would pass and she would smile and laugh,\r\nJust like the rest of us,\r\nBut deep down inside, she’s suffocating...\r\n\r\n\r\n*The world kept turning,\r\n People kept on living, each and every day. \r\n Hell, who’s giving a damn,\r\n Where she’s going.\r\n Nobody cared that she stopped breathing.\r\n\r\n So she was determined,\r\n Made up her mind to change her unkind fate,\r\n And so she’d set all the wrongs, \r\n Where they belong.\r\n She’d run up close to the stars.*\r\n\r\n\r\nWhen she turned seventeen,\r\nHer daddy went to prison.\r\nNot anybody could rescue her vision.\r\n\r\nNow she was left alone,\r\nHer mommy passed away, her daddy gone.\r\nDaddy, you scare me but please don’t leave me this broken home.\r\n\r\n*', '', 336, '', 'Austin', '失物招領 Lost and Found', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-06-16 00:44:44', '2015-03-12 13:42:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
